{
  "stem": "13817.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "You would be sent to a so-called-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to the east in the eastern part of Europe, which was Poland, where there would be cities.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "There were cities being built where just Jews lived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "All your furniture would be shipped afterwards or stored for you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And everything would be just like normal, only you would be living only under Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So we didn't know anything what was going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "No idea.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Before your telephones were taken away, and-- when they-- for instance, when they came and took the telephones away, right by the telephone we had a, a, a stamp collection which was very valuable.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "My dad had already started it, and they took that away too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They stole it, actually, because he wasn't supposed to.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But we wouldn't have dared to go to the Gestapo and say, the guy who picked up the phone, he picked up the-- he would say, you-- no, no, no German steals.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Only Jews steal, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "So this was the other deal what happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Well, then, we went-- we actually took more than 100 marks each.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "We sewed the money into clothing and hiding it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "So we-- when we got-- so we came to the railway station, and we were put on trains.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And the train took off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And we didn't have any idea where we were going.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And after two nights and three days, or two days, two and a half days, we-- the train all of a sudden came to a stop.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And as we got out, we walked through the mud, about a half a foot or a foot deep.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "With your belongings, you were walking into an area, which was a slum area, which was encircled with, with barbed wires, guards all around it.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
